nodes.text: A insectoid pirate who was present in the courtroom of Captain Gir Kybo Ren-Cha on the planet Tarnoonga.
A member of the the crew of Kybo Ren-Cha, this pirate witnessed the interrogation of Jann Tosh before the young miner was taken by skiff to be thrown to the Miridon.

This pirate, whose physical appearance is similar to the Brizzit species, appeared only in the book The Pirates of Tarnoonga: A Droid Adventure and was not present in the Pirates of Tarnoonga television episode.
